item.title: FrogsTicket
item.description: This is a Discord bot for ticket system. Allows you to create a discord, a ticket system on your server, namely, an appeal to the administration or the task of important questions in a separate chat with the administration

item.title: FexCubes
item.description: This project was made to show how I started my career as a web developer and web designer, as well as to prove to myself that you do not need to be afraid to expose your code for viewing.
